<span class="rating">Rating<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content" >
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'>Emacs のミニバッファから。</pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>(defun input-checker (n s)
  (interactive &quot;nTime(second): \nsString: &quot;)
  (let ((c (read-char (concat &quot;input(&quot; s &quot;)=&gt;&quot;))))
    (push c unread-command-events))
  (with-timeout (n (message &quot;TIME OUT&quot;))
    (let ((input (read-string (concat &quot;input(&quot; s &quot;)=&gt;&quot;))))
      (message (if (string= input s) &quot;OK&quot; &quot;NG&quot;)))))
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
